# Checkpoints directory
# .agents/sessions/checkpoints/.gitkeep
#
# Per-session checkpoint files are created HERE by /plan (Step 5.5).
# Each session gets: .agents/sessions/<session-id>/checkpoints/
# Actual checkpoint files are named: <N>.md where N is the tool call count trigger.
#
# Checkpoint file format:
# ---
# # Auto-Checkpoint — <timestamp>
# Session: <session-id>
# Tool calls executed: <N>
# Trigger: tool call #<N>
#
# ## Task States at Checkpoint
# - [x] task_001 -> SDET: Done ✅ (92% confidence)
# - [/] task_002 -> Backend Architect: IN PROGRESS
# - [ ] task_003 -> Security Engineer: Pending
#
# ## Agents Active
# Backend Architect — task_002 (~12 min elapsed)
#
# ## Files Modified So Far
# [CREATED] src/services/auth.service.ts
# [MODIFIED] src/routes/api/login.ts
#
# ## Next Action On Resume
# Continue task_002 — Backend Architect is mid-implementation of auth service.
# ---
